               <msContents>
                  <summary>Book of Hours of Abba Giyorgis, መጽሐፈ፡ ሰዓታት፡  ዘአባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, produced in the government scriptorium</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="82r" facs="003">Fols 1r–82r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3575Mashaf">Maṣḥafa
                                                  saʿātāt</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሰዳዴሆሙ፡ ለአጋንንት፡ እምየማንነ፡ ወእምፀጋምነ፡ ወእዛቲ፡ መካንነ፡ ይርኅቁ፡ እምኔነ፡ ለእለ፡ ይፀብዕዋ፡ ለነፍስነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
