                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                           <foreign xml:lang="gez">ገብርኤል፡</foreign>
                        </seg>
                        <desc>The words Mary and Gabriel are rubricated. Many words are abbreviated in red ink</desc>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#1r #27v #62r #66v" facs="003 030 064 069">folss. 1r, 27v, 62r, 66v, </locus> (haräg);
                  <locus target="#36r #48r #52r #56r #62r #70r #81v #82r" facs="038 050 054 058 064 072 084 084">36r, 48r, 52r, 56r, 62r, 70r, 81v, 82r</locus> (multiple full stops)
                  </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                          <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001"> f. ir(ecto), upper</locus>
                          <desc type="RecordTransaction">List of witnesses in an unspecified transaction‎</desc>
                          </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                          <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002"> f. iv(erso), lower</locus>
                          <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002">iir(ecto)</locus>
                           <desc type="RecordDistribution">Record of an inheritance, in Amharic, from Wäldä Maryam to his children</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                          <locus target="#66v" facs="069"> f. 66v and passim</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">the owner is Häbtä Wäld</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                          <locus target="#82r" facs="084">Fol. 82r</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">mentions owner, HäbtäW äld and scribe, Zär’a Yoḥannǝs</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                        <locus target="#82v" facs="085">Fol. 82v</locus>
                          <desc type="RecordTransaction">Record of transaction, exchange of a “Belgic” rifle for another type ‎‎(mǝnǝšǝr) of rifle, in Amharic, with a fingerprint and signature ‎surrounding the fingerprint‎</desc>
                          </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>Several lines of evidence point to this manuscript being produced in the government scriptorium</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                          <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001"> f. ir(ecto), upper</locus>
                           <desc type="RecordTransaction">List of witnesses in an unspecified transaction</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                          <locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="002">Fol. iiv(erso)</locus>
                           <desc>blank</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4">
                           <desc>Identified in the insurance hand list as Case 67/1</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e5">
                          <locus target="#ii #4 #7 #10 #13 #18 #23 #27 #36 #42 #52 #58" facs="002 006 009 012 015 020 025 029 038 044 054 060">Fols. ii, 4, 7, 10, 13, 18, 23, 27, 36, 42, 52, 58</locus>
