                       </item>
                       <item xml:id="e6">
                         <locus target="#1 #8 #11 #15 #19 #25 #30 #39 #48 #62" facs="003 010 013 016 021 027 032 041 050 064">Fols. 1, 8, 11, 15, 19, 25, 30, 39, 48, 62</locus>
                        <desc>green yarn is sewn into the fore edge as navigation system</desc>
                       </item>
                        <item xml:id="e7">
                           <desc>Numbered quires: quires 1–6, <locus target="#q1 #q2 #q3 #q4 #q5 #q6">fols. q1, q2, q3, q4, q5, q6</locus>
                            </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e8">
                          <locus target="#23v #25r #28v #30r" facs="026 027 031 032">Fols. 23v, 25r, 28v, 30r</locus>
                           <desc>
                            etc., words of text are written interlinearly
                          </desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id="e9">
                          <locus target="#81r" facs="083">Fol. 81r</locus>
                          <desc>lines of text are written interlinearly</desc>
                          </item>
                          <item xml:id="e10">
                          <locus target="#20v" facs="023"> f. 20v, col. 2, line 2</locus>
                          <desc>lines are text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted</desc>
